{"id":163287,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011622/","date":"2011-06-23T13:30:30Z","modified":"2011-06-23T13:30:30Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/6/22","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span>@yigroup</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/06/23/world/asia/23artist.html?_r=3\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">艾未未被释放</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">（</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110622/ap_on_re_as/as_china_human_rights\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/afp/20110622/wl_asia_afp/chinaartrights\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">法新社</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110622/people_nm/us_china_artist_13\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/news/world/asia/article3071574.ece\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《泰晤士报》</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/artanddesign/2011/jun/22/ai-weiwei-freed-by-chinese-police\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/8432272/China-breaks-silence-on-Ai-Weiweis-detention.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/arts-post/post/chinese-artist-ai-weiwei-released/2011/06/22/AGBqJ0fH_blog.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华盛顿邮报》</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/world/la-fg-china-artist-20110623,0,4814130.story\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《洛杉矶时报》</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Global-News/2011/0622/Artist-Ai-Weiwei-released-Chinese-police-say?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+feeds%2Fworld+%28Christian+Science+Monitor+%7C+World%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《基督教科学箴言报》</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,2079300,00.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《时代》周刊</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/asia-pacific/renowned-chinese-activist-ai-weiwei-out-on-bail/article2070777/?utm_medium=Feeds%3A%20RSS%2FAtom&#038;utm_source=Asia-Pacific&#038;utm_content=2070777\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《环球邮报》</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.google.com/url?sa=t&#038;source=web&#038;cd=1&#038;ved=0CCQQFjAA&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FInternational%2Fchinese-artist-ai-weiwei-detained-missing%2Fstory%3Fid%3D13289713&#038;ei=lE4CTtLOMZDUgAe7ttjNBA&#038;usg=AFQjCNHgB-rzLm2MwB4YJmifaVmWmQ-jAg\">ABC</a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://behindthewall.msnbc.msn.com/_news/2011/06/22/6918034-ai-weiwei-released-from-detention\">NBC</a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2011/06/22/501364/main20073301.shtml\">CBS</a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.google.com/url?sa=t&#038;source=web&#038;cd=3&#038;sqi=2&#038;ved=0CDIQFjAC&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2011%2FWORLD%2Fasiapcf%2F06%2F22%2Fchina.dissident%2Findex.html&#038;ei=wk4CTsy3FYrpgQehpd2iBw&#038;usg=AFQjCNHX2lK4sHzuRYJBVZOriDj8jybdyw\">CNN</a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">都有报道）</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/06/23/world/asia/23iht-letter23.html?partner=rssnyt\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">对中国的自拆发起挑战</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——艺术家郭建的作品描绘了天安门广场被拆迁的场面</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">法新社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/afp/20110622/wl_asia_afp/chinapoliticshistorycommunism\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">重庆，中国的红色复兴之都</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“年轻人学会唱红歌后，会取得思想进步，也开始变得遵守纪律”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110622/ap_on_re_as/as_china_bribery_battle_1\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国对受欢迎的举报贿赂网站实施管制</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——新近冒出来的几家举报收受贿赂行为的网站陆续关张</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华盛顿季刊》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twq.com/11winter/docs/11winter_Shambaugh.pdf\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">对付矛盾中的中国</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">（</span><span>20</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">页</span><span>PDF</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">报告）——中国的外交政策显示出互相矛盾的重点，美国应采取现实主义对策</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">卡内基国际和平基金会</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.carnegieendowment.org/publications/index.cfm?fa=view&#038;id=44739&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+carnegie%2Fchina+%28DC+-+Region+-+China%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">穷人将继承世界</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——发展中国家的崛起不仅扩大了繁荣的阵营，也引起了巨大的紧张</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交学者</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/china-power/2011/06/20/china%E2%80%99s-middle-east-diplomacy/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的中东外交</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“中国在中东问题上一向与阿拉伯联盟保持一致；现在阿盟与卡扎菲撇清了，中国自然会改变立场”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交学者</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/2011/06/22/china-looms-over-russia-far-east/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国在俄国远东地区盘踞</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——虽然双方贸易关系紧密，但对军工技术和中国工人大量涌入方面的担心可能会伤害到双边关系</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交事务委员会</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cfr.org/china/regional-turbulence-over-south-china-sea/p25319?cid=rss-asia-regional_turbulence_over_south-062211&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+region%2Fasia+%28CFR.org+-+Regions+-+Asia%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">关于南中国海地区争端的问答</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——介绍了南海争端的背景以及美国的立场和对策</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国外人</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://chinabystander.wordpress.com/2011/06/21/the-persistence-of-party-power-over-chinas-private-enterprises/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国私企中的共产党势力</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——在中国私营机构中有</span><span>280</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万个党组织，“自由经济”没有不受党领导的自由</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">国家亚洲研究局</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nbr.org/publications/element.aspx?id=497\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">台湾的未来：越来越窄的海峡</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">（</span><span>22</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">页</span><span>PDF</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">报告）——台湾自身的弱点和美国不断减少的支持，使得台湾除了接受大陆日益增加的影响外别无选择</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110622/pl_nm/us_china_usa_cyberwar\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国称中美之间没有网络战</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——崔天凯表示中美之间对于黑客攻击行为的态度是一致的</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/06/23/world/asia/23china.html?partner=rss&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国警告美国不要插手南海争端</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“个别国家在玩火，希望美国不要引火烧身”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经贸动向】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110622/ap_on_bi_ge/as_china_inflation\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国政府称通货膨胀在六月会进一步增加</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——国家发改委表示六月通货膨胀率会比五月更高</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福布斯》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.forbes.com/timferguson/2011/06/21/865/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国神奇的</span>8%<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">增速</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国实体经济的发展面临被其它关键领域（如房地产）的活动与价格所扼杀的局面</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/06/23/business/global/23rail.html?partner=rss&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">高速铁路将改变中国</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——尽管高铁不尽如人意，但它会给中国带来真实的经济效益，并对欧美</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">构成挑战</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>–<span>  </span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/06/20/on_the_economy_be_careful_what_you_wish_for\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">要清楚自己在经济上想要什么</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——全球经济实力正在快速落入中国手中，美国应付得了吗？</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-06-22/yahoo-bet-on-alibaba-shows-risk-in-china-s-legal-gray-areas.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">雅虎的阿里巴巴困境显示出中国法律灰色地带的风险</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——对于外国企业来说，想了解中国的规矩不是件容易的事情</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【社会百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国见红</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://seeingredinchina.com/2011/06/22/the-plight-of-the-mentally-disabled-in-china/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国智障人员的悲惨处境</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——不少自闭症儿童被作为弱智对待，有些智障人员甚至被拐卖成奴工</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国外人</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://chinabystander.wordpress.com/2011/06/16/the-lessons-of-chinas-disappearing-lakes/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">消失的中国湖泊带给我们的教训</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——城市化和工业化改变了中国水资源管理的优先顺序，其环境影响不容忽视</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交学者</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/china-power/2011/06/14/resistance-futile-in-chinese-class/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在中国的课堂上，抵制是没用的</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“虽然课堂上活动很多，但是却没有什么真正意义上的学习，老师似乎也无视学生们的存在”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交学者</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/china-power/2011/06/16/sending-chinese-problems-abroad/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">把中国的问题送出国</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——为什么冒着风险富裕起来的中国人，也愿意冒险把自己的孩子交给不同文化环境中的陌生人来教育呢？</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/8591881/Chinas-single-children-rapidly-becoming-overweight.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的独生子女正在快速发胖</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——他们的父母在变胖速度上也不甘落后，全球排名仅次于墨西哥</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"><br /></span></p>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-4527133951165698172?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":720,"categories":[1],"tags":[]}